Dole ne lambu ya zama mai danshi da hanyar samun ruwa.
Don haka, yana da kyau idan an haƙa rijiya ko wata hanyar samun ruwa mafi kusa, dogaro da ruwan sama don ban ruwa, wannan tsohon yayi ne.
